{"tid":2163850,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"弊！尼馬交換波衫決賽唔踢得？","createTime":"2020-08-19T01:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T09:32:34.000Z","uid":72497,"like":291,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"689d3e9d563480f8b304eb052e43865ecb4d53a1","tid":2163850,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:52:12.000Z","msg":"巴黎聖日耳門球星尼馬在歐聯賽後與對手交換波衫，或要隔離12日缺席歐聯決賽。<br />\n<br />\n法甲豪門巴黎聖日耳門周二於歐聯4強戰以3:0淘汰萊比錫，球會史上首次殺入歐聯決賽，巴西球星尼馬（Neymar）賽後興奮過了頭，竟然與對方球員哈史頓保交換波衫，這可能令他錯過下周日的冠軍戰。 <br />\n<br />\n根據歐洲足協的規定，賽事於新冠疫情下閉門作賽，一旦球員交換波衫，將要進行12天自我隔離，以免出現病毒傳染。曼聯名宿里奧費迪南在評述時也很意外：「起初我覺得他不會真的交換，再看重播才相信是真的。」 尼馬對萊比錫雖然沒有入球，但表現十分活躍，上半場射門中門柱，更助攻迪馬利亞射入2:0的一球。"},{"pid":"1dcf5db83c0fb4ceffde44c4727920247ac944eb","tid":2163850,"uid":166474,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:55:05.000Z","msg":"唔係驗晒negative先比落場咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d8d48da89c073f21862f25ed1bdee076680504","tid":2163850,"uid":72497,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1dcf5db83c0fb4ceffde44c4727920247ac944eb","tid":2163850,"uid":166474,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:55:05.000Z","msg":"唔係驗晒negative先比落場咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:57:00.000Z","msg":"雙重保險啩"},{"pid":"2ef554c3b4a1057205b730af44fe9a72ba86a84d","tid":2163850,"uid":288884,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:57:29.000Z","msg":"笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7cec48b673a8568d8a2876b7f7c01c434f3c63f","tid":2163850,"uid":166474,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T01:58:58.000Z","msg":"去PSG三年傷多過踢, 最重要果場無傷都唔踢得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse